# Cursor Rules for smart-fitness-booking-agent-demo

You are working on "smart-fitness-booking-agent-demo", a TypeScript, React, Vite project.

## Guidelines

- Write clean, readable code with minimal comments
- Follow existing patterns in the codebase
- Prefer editing existing files over creating new ones
- Run tests after making changes
- Keep imports organized
- Use strict TypeScript — no `any` types
- Prefer interfaces over type aliases for objects
- Use functional components with hooks
- Prefer server components in Next.js App Router
